{"tid":2417842,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【曾傳車震】Baby被爆三亞約會男星 鄧倫再捲緋聞","createTime":"2021-02-22T07:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T07:41:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58dcf9b2bab8a7dfec089c8943fe0a91a199cfc7","tid":2417842,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Z1ZRIqwRLo79lVB5oDYWJg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/23cc0f80-74c4-11eb-96cf-9ce7c94c5f05\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZ1ZRIqwRLo79lVB5oDYWJg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2F23cc0f80-74c4-11eb-96cf-9ce7c94c5f05&h=d31585c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女星Angelababy與黃曉明結婚多年屢傳婚變，早前有指男方夜店攬女，加上Baby以「黃先生」稱呼老公，婚變傳聞愈煲愈勁！近日有網友爆料指於三亞海棠灣巧遇Baby衝浪，身旁有一名男星作伴，不過嗰個唔係黃曉明，而係「鄧姓男星」！網民紛紛揣測男星身份係鄧倫，過去與Baby合作劇集《我的真朋友》曾傳緋聞，甚至傳出車震，男方工作室曾否認並叫網民唔好散播謠言，如今再次傳出緋聞，未知今次會點樣澄清呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tmSrVmME71Es4JjfoeEx6A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-02/49199f00-74c4-11eb-bdfc-b82b73a08f7a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FtmSrVmME71Es4JjfoeEx6A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-02%2F49199f00-74c4-11eb-bdfc-b82b73a08f7a&h=e5496f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過年時Baby被拍到現身機場，帶仔仔小海綿飛三亞度假，現時未有回程消息，似乎仍然度假當中。"},{"pid":"9a7d2779f948e303ba7f90ce300354bb22794803","tid":2417842,"uid":23170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"做乜執到咁似變性人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}